node.title: SH1 reopens near Whangārei after vehicle fire forced closure
node.description: The major Northland highway has reopened at Hūkerenui between Whangārei and Kawakawa.
node.content:
["", "
Photo: Supplied / Erica Shaw
", "A vehicle on fire at Hūkerenui between Whangārei and Kawakawa.", "The major Northland highway has reopened in Hūkerenui between Whangārei and Kawakawa.", "Emergency services responded to reports of a vehicle fire in the area at 7:15am.", "Police temporarily closed State Highway 1 near Crows Nest Road in both directions while the scene was cleared.", "No injuries have been reported."]
